---
title: Pork and Veggie Chow Mein with Toasted Sesame Seeds
description: Bust out your chopsticks for this deliciously sweet, spicy, umami chow mein dish! Stir-fried peppers and cabbage get a fragrant boost from fresh ginger and toasty sesame oil, but it's the soy-sweet chili sauce that will really make your taste buds sing!
